longBusinessSummary: A1 Group, Inc. operates as an electronic cigarette company in the United States. The company's electronic cigarettes are battery-powered products that enable users to inhale nicotine vapor without smoke, tar, ash, or carbon monoxide. It offers disposable electronic cigarettes in multiple sizes, puff counts, styles, flavors, and nicotine strengths; rechargeable electronic cigarettes that use replaceable cartridges; and rechargeable vaporizers for use with electronic cigarette solutions, dry herbs, or leaves. The company sells its electronic cigarettes and accessories through the Website a1vapors.com, as well as through two retail locations in the greater Miami area to cigarette smokers and hookah smokers from the ages of 18 and more. A1 Group, Inc. was founded in 2012 and is based in Carlsbad, California.
